---
title: Sweet & Smoky Chicken with Buttery Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: Pork chops are always a weeknight winner. They’re satisfying, speedy, and versatile, which is why our chefs are always brainstorming new ways to take ’em to the next level. The kicker this week: a fresh ginger and apricot jam pan sauce to drizzle over the chops. On the side, there’s roasted green beans and buttery jasmine rice (perfect for catching any runoff sauce).

